data.description: Welcoming 3BR, 2BA ranch-style brick home in Green Cove Springs off Russell Rd. Enjoy 2062 Sq Ft of comfort. Fully fenced yard with a concrete driveway leading to covered parking. Enter the home through the screened front porch, complete with a porch swing for sunset relaxation. The spacious living room has the warmth of a charming wood-burning fireplace. A unique feature is the flex space with a private entrance, perfect for generational living, or primary suite. The kitchen offers a breakfast bar and a separate dining room. The expansive yard allows for a potential garage or ample space for your toys. No HOA restrictions. Only 2 owners and has had some upgrades. Nestled in the Hidden Waters Community, it provides a rural feel while remaining close to shopping and restaurants. Property has a canal accessible through rear, inviting kayaking adventures leading to Black Creek.
